    "body": "### Description\n\nI have switched to the new 0.11 setup, both clangd and lua_ls work find. After inspecting lsp log, it seems csharp_ls is not looking for .sln and .csproj in root dir but in the current working directory. If I manually call the old `lspconfig.csharp_ls.setup{}`, It correctly use the root dir.",
